danw@tekig5.pen.tek.com (Daniel E Wilson) writes:


>  Can anyone tell me where to find descriptions of the MD5 and
>  IDEA algorithms detailed enough to write code from? I would
>  prefer a document that I could FTP from the net.


Dr Dobb's Journal December 93 contains a good description by Bruce
Schneier of IDEA. The C source code is available in the directory:

	ftp.mv.com:/pub/ddj

You could also look at the PGP distribution.

